data.description: Look at this amazing two story property in desirable Ahwatukee location! With desert landscaping and 2 car garage, this home will conquer you the minute you step out of the car! Perfectly flowing interior boasts soaring ceilings, tons of natural light, cozy family room and bright dining. Lovely kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, tons of maple cabinets, plenty of granite counters space, custom back-splash, pantry and breakfast nook. Master suite has vaulted ceilings that add to the spacious feel, closet, and immaculate bath w/double sinks, closet and tiled shower. Beautiful backyard offers nice covered patio, sparkling blue pool and deck where you can relax & take some sun between swims. Don't wait any longer, a beauty like this won't last long!
